ğŸ”· PYRAMID PATTERNS

(Columns = 2*n - 1)

1ï¸âƒ£8ï¸âƒ£ Pyramid Left Edge
j == n - i + 1

1ï¸âƒ£9ï¸âƒ£ Pyramid Right Edge
