ğŸ”» INVERTED PYRAMIDS
2ï¸âƒ£2ï¸âƒ£ Inverted Pyramid
j >= i && j <= 2*n - i

2ï¸âƒ£3ï¸âƒ£ Hollow Inverted Pyramid
