ğŸ’ DIAMOND PATTERNS

(Combination of pyramid + inverted pyramid)

2ï¸âƒ£4ï¸âƒ£ Diamond Pattern
Upper:
j >= n - i + 1 && j <= n + i - 1

Lower:
j >= i - n + 1 && j <= 3*n - i - 1

2ï¸âƒ£5ï¸âƒ£ Hollow Diamond Pattern
j == n - i + 1 ||
j == n + i - 1 ||
j == i - n + 1 ||
j == 3*n - i - 1

